-1 Campaigner~
Campaigners are the veterans of the realm's armies.  For one reason or
another, they band together, live, fight, and die together in the maintained
armies of the various nations.  Whether a Child of the Light, an Illianer
Campanion, or a Queen's Guardsman, all Campaigners are duly trained soldiers
who work better in groups than they do on their own.  As such, a lone
soldier might not prove to be much of a threat, but a group of Campaigners
is a force to be reckoned with.  
 
