51 HEAL_RATES~
This help files includes rules for attributing heal/OPU regen rates to
both objects and rooms.  (Referred to as heal rates)

1) Heal rates of 100% are the mud norm, below 100% will cause a player
to regen slower than normal, above will be faster.
2) Portable furnitures may NEVER have a heal rate exceeding 115%.
3) No area may offer more than 2 opportunities to a heal rate of
   130% or above.  These rates should be rare and extremely discouraged.
4) There should NEVER be a heal rate exceeding 150% in an area.
5) Any heal rate 130% or above must be flagged safe, law, and open to
   the public.  Ie, no private, guild_only, or sex_only.
6) Objects/ rooms dropping a player's heal rate below 30% must be
   approved by Council and have VERY good rationale.
 
