Mayene is a small city-state which rests on a peninsula east of Tear.
Although it is an independent nation, Tear claims it as a province, despite
loud protests from Mayene.  The primary source of Mayene's wealth and what
little independence it possesses is the secret oilfish shoals.  The lamp oil
which is produced from oilfish rivals that produced from the olives grown by
Tear, Illian, and Tarabon.  No Tairen knows the secret location of the
oilfish shoals, and Mayene will kill to insure that none ever do.

