the Paendrag name.  The current "First" of Mayene is Berelain sur Paendrag,
a young and beautiful ruler who is extremely capable in more than one
respect, and who acted as the regent of Cairhien for a short while.

The sigil of Mayene is a golden hawk in flight.  Its banner is a Golden Hawk
in flight on a field of blue.  Called Paendrag's Banner by Mayeners, it is
fringed in gold when the First is present.  The capital city is Mayene.

  See also COUNTRIES.

