0 MULTIPLAYING~
Multiplaying occurs when one person a player logs on more than a single
character at a time.  For either IC or OOC reasons, multiplaying is ILLEGAL
and not to be done.  Punishment may include the deletion of a character,
deletion of all characters involved, sitebanning, or worse.  
 
While it is understandable that several friends might pool down into
a lab to mud together, it is advisable to space yourselves to avoid
harassment and questioning by IMMS.  For a good rule of thumb, you are
guilty until proven innocent.  Tread lightly.
 
