0 ROLEPLAY RP~
Roleplay, or RP for short, is a very fun activity that is very much
encouraged on this mud. It is just a way of doing things according to
different rules than those that our real world enforce. RP is acting IC and
interacting with other players.

RP can be used as a noun and a verb, depending on the use. If someone says,
"My character's RP is that he was born here, blah blah", then they are saying
that this character or person acts as though this is what happened to them
and this is their life/experience so far in the WoT world. If someone says,
"We had some fun RP yesterday!", then they are stating that they interacted
ICly with some other players, and had fun doing it (of course).

RP is a skill, and usually not simply "gifts" to certain people. It is a
combination of imagination and creativity. Practice makes perfect in RP,
also. The more you do it, the better you will become. It helps some people
to actually imagine that you are the character, and have lived their life,
and then simply react accordingly.

  See also: IC, OOC, WHEEL OF TIME, ARCHETYPE
~

