0 SAIDIN SAIDAR~
The Wheel of Time is driven by the True Source, from which both halves of
the One Power can be drawn.  Working both together and against eachother, it
is Saidin and Saidar which provide the driving force that turns the Wheel. 
Saidin is the male half of the One Power, while Saidar is the female half. 
Though the two halves of the Power work to drive forth the Wheel, they are
as different as night and day.  The differences between the two aspects of
the Power vary so greatly, that it is impossible for a woman to teach a man
in the use of the Power and vice versa.  In fact, similar feats may be
attempted through use of the Power, but the mechanics behind them alone
could still or kill a channeler if it was attempted in the fashion of the
complimentary Power.  

At the moment, the male half of the Power, Saidin, has been horribly Tainted
by the Dark One.  What exactly this Taint is or how to cure it is unknown,
but one thing is for certain- no man can channel the Power for long without
the fear of death or insanity taking him.  (This IS hard-coded).  
 
See also CHANNELING, SEIZE, EMBRACE
