While rogues are normally an underhanded lot, Thief arch-types spend most of
their time working towards advancing their own whims through subterfuge
rather than combat.  As such, they are very sneaky, but also not too
powerful in a physical confrontation.  Still the have means at their
disposal to get by.  Characters studying under this group will gain the
following skills (upon level requirements):
[0 ] pick lock   
[1 ] backstab
[2 ] hide  
[3 ] steal
[4 ] dirt kick    
[5 ] haggle
[6 ] peek   
[7 ] trip
