0 TRAVELLING~
With a Talent in Travelling it is possible to manipulate the Pattern to
traverse space in a matter of moments or heartbeats that would otherwise
take weeks or months to travel on horseback or on foot.  
~

0 TREAT~
By treating yourself or another, you apply the basics of healing to them.
Weak pulpices, bandages, and bracings all go into the tendering of a wound,
and the treat skill ensures proper knowledge in their application.  When
wounded, you can be treated once, but further wounds can also be treated
after they are inflicted.  

Having another treat you yields a higher healing effect than treating
yourself.  
~

-1 TRIP~
TRIP

A popular method of grounding one's opponent by rogues, this skill may be
used by warriors as well.  A dastardly attack, trip knocks over one's
oppenent, partially stunning them.  While grounded, players have penalties
to their attacks and flee chances.  Tripping your opponent bases the
player's dexterities against each other, generally agile players can avoid a
trip.  

Players chosing the Sovin'Dore weapons group have an additional bonus, when
they successfully trip a player, they are quick to apply an additional
stamping, furthering the damage.  
