-1 TROLLOCS~
Trollocs were created before The War of the Shadow to serve as soldiers in
the Dark One's armies.  A strange combination of human and animal genetic
material, Trollocs possess strength and speed far beyond that of either the
animal or human parts of their heritage.  Standing from eight to ten feet in
height, they are almost as fast as horses, and are extremely vicious
fighters.  Possessing the facial features of their animal heritage, Trollocs
have a very limited intelligence, little discipline, and all the worst of
human characteristics.  Cruel and ruthless, they have been known to eat
almost anything they find, often murdering each other too fill their
cookpots.  Because of this, it is generally necessary for them to be
controlled by a Myrddraal.

