The nation of Saldaea is the largest of the Blightborder nations.  Flanked
by the Aryth Ocean and Kandor, it is larger than Shienar and Arafel
combined.  Like all Borderland nations, Saldaea has a strong military
tradition, which is embodied by its cavalry.  The Saldaean cavalry is widely
