In most military commands, the cavalry is often the most feared unit. 
Made up of soldiers mounted upon well-trained steeds, the cavalry is quick
and deadly.  Often companies are deployed in order to help secure an area or
provide a quick strike against an enemies' weakest fortified area.  The
lightning speed of the cavarly is their greatest asset.  Players who chose
this battle group will gain the following skills (upon level requirements): 
 
